[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61294/?]Lora Preset For RaceMenu[/url][/size]







How to install:

1.Download file

2.Unpack file to: The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim/data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets

3. Run Skyrim

4.Open racemenu

5.Set race to Dark Elf

6.Set slider for the Preset Slot on slot 12

8.Press F9

9.Have Fun!
